tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE interventions_data (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  intervention_name VARCHAR(255),
  intervention_date DATE,
  effectiveness_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE patients (   patient_id INT,   patient_name VARCHAR(50),   age INT,   diagnosis VARCHAR(100),   admission_date DATE );

CREATE TABLE interventions (   intervention_id INT,   intervention_name VARCHAR(50),   patient_id INT,   intervention_date DATE,   success_rate FLOAT );

CREATE TABLE patient_records (
    patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    intervention_id UUID REFERENCES interventions(intervention_id)
);

CREATE TABLE program_evaluation (
    evaluation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    intervention_id UUID REFERENCES interventions(intervention_id),
    patient_id UUID REFERENCES patient_records(patient_id),
    evaluation_date DATE,
    satisfaction_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  diagnosis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE outcomes (
  outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  outcome_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  outcome_description TEXT,
  intervention_id INT,
  program_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  outcome_value FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  date_of_birth DATE
)

CREATE TABLE interventions (
  intervention_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  intervention_name VARCHAR(100),
  description TEXT,
  intervention_type VARCHAR(50),
  effectiveness_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE healthcare_providers (
  provider_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_name VARCHAR(50),
  specialization VARCHAR(50),
  contact_number VARCHAR(15),
  location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE patient_intervention_history (
  history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  intervention_id INT,
  date_of_intervention DATE,
  outcome TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE program_evaluation (
  evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(100),
  evaluation_date DATE,
  outcome_evaluation TEXT,
  effectiveness_score FLOAT
)
